## Ministry of Agriculture-Animal health

## Additional measures

- Compensation
- bonus-malus system (owners, who implements certain extra measures get higher compensation), base rate is 60%
- the compensation rate is maximum 80% of the proposed amount for poultry keepers
- Legal requirement to keep a certain distance between existing and new holdings

<!-- image -->

<!-- image -->

## Ministry of Agriculture-Animal health

## Additional measures

- Aid for ceasing operations
- o stopped keeping waterfowl for 3 years
- o 50 000 EUR/farmer
- o 201 waterfowl farmers
- o highly affected area
- Transformation of foie-gras waterfowl sector
- o multi-phase
- o 24-40 % goose sector
- o 50-100 % duck sector
- o movement of waterfowls decreased, which may reduce the number of outbreaks

